'''Mithlond, Göteborgs Tolkiensällskap''' is the Swedish Tolkien Society of [[wikipedia:Gothenburg|Gothenburg]]. It was founded in [[1981]], hived off from [[Forodrim]]. The association publishes ''[[Elostirion (magazine)|Elostirion]]''.

Mithlond is composed of several guilds, each devoted to a specific task. These inlude languages, art and handicraft, gaming, food, etc.
